{
  "stem": "21310.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would sell it and just-- depends on the soup kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there was, as I mentioned, soup kitchen established.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But people were just dying in, in, in the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The most horrid [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] things were the, the people who-- children, you know, lying in the, in the street, swollen from hunger.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some, some kids were just going, and especially towards the evening, and, and yelling, throw down a piece bread, a piece of moldy bread, you know, in, in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was just heart breaking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You could give them-- maybe if you had a piece of bread, you could give them a, a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so, so there were-- especially the people who were refugees from the surrounding towns who were poor to start with and couldn't help themselves.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But there was a, a quite a robust economy going on in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was like an underground economy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "People were making all kind-- well, first of all, there were some factories established.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We called them shops.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And some of them were run by Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And some of them were run by Jews, really, who had some-- not connection.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the German was supervising or somehow, they were all going for Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But there was the brush makers and the all kinds of stuff.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were making utensils out of metal that was smuggled in from some downed airplanes or so.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were making spoons and forks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And, and that was being exported to the Aryan side of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then I remember, they were making .",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Boots we all had boots.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The, the sole was wood.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
